n_Berger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ann-Katrin_Berger\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They also held a slender lead in possession over the 90 minutes, but they were unable to create any meaningful opportunities with the ball.\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia was later made to pay by their opponents, who took advantage of their own attacking opportunities to take themselves out of reach.\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1135, \"end\": 1144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.499044585832757e-14, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Matildas' shaky set piece defence was punished once more in the 64th minute with striker Lea Schuller's header getting past Arnold on this occasion.\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1370, \"end\": 1373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lea_Salonga\", \"score\": 0.965967043698963, \"rank\": 0.03523083368054346, \"text\": \"Lea\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lea_Salonga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lea_Salonga\"}, {\"begin\": 1405, \"end\": 1411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\", \"score\": 0.9129723922301224, \"rank\": 0.09531373229724528, \"text\": \"Arnold\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just four minutes later, winger Jule Brand, who had caused havoc for the Matildas throughout the game, put the match 