re.\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1832, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think at times we were well on top and let two set pieces affect the game in a very negative way.\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1932, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are things that we can fix nice and quickly, which is good.\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 1998, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But we just need to be better,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2040, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are a good team.\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We did it to ourselves in the end.\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2099, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We conceded two set pieces.\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are usually much, much better on set pieces.\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is a wake-up call and it is not to our standard and we need to be better for the next game and turn this tournament around.\\\"\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2303, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia have Zambia in their next match, a must-win encounter as they still have the fifth-ranked United States to face.\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2305, \"end\": 2314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.499044585832757e-14, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2320, \"end\": 2326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999996521183, \"rank\": 3.4252088380520847e-10, \"text\": \"Zambia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia_national_football_